<reference id="rrefgetdbpropfunc" xml:lang="pt-br">
<title>SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_GET_DATABASE_PROPERTY</title>
<refbody>
<section>
<p>A função <codeph>SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_GET_DATABASE_PROPERTY</codeph>
retorna o valor da propriedade especificada por <codeph>KEY</codeph>,
do banco de dados na conexão corrente.</p>
</section>
<section>
<title>Sintaxe</title>
<codeblock>VARCHAR(32762) SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_GET_DATABASE_PROPERTY(IN KEY VARCHAR(128))</codeblock>
<p>Retorna erro se <codeph>KEY</codeph> for nulo.</p>
</section>
<section>
<title>Exemplo</title>
<codeblock>VALUES SYSCS_UTIL.SYSCS_GET_DATABASE_PROPERTY('cadeia_com_valor_da_chave');</codeblock>
</section>
</refbody>
</reference>
